<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>SuperCool - Propose Your Thinking</title>
    <!-- Font Awesome CDN -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/5.15.4/css/all.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./project.css">
    <style>
    * {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
    }
    
    body {
        background-color: #f8f8f8;
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    }

    .header {
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
        text-align: center;
    }
    
    .top-bar {
        background-color: #d62828; /* Red theme color */
        color: #fff;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        text-align: center;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: space-between;
    }

    .top-bar p {
        font-style: italic;
        margin-left: 10px;
    }

    .logo {
        width: 40px;
        height: 40px;
        border-radius: 50%;
    }
    
    .centered-text {
        position: relative;
        z-index: 1;
        color: #d62828; /* Red theme color */
        margin-top: 20px; /* Adjusted margin */
        font-size: 1.5em; /* Adjusted font size */
        font-weight: bold; /* Adjusted font weight */
        text-transform: uppercase; /* Adjusted text case */
    }
    
    .wave-container {
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
    }
    
    .wave {
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        width: 100%;
    }

    .card-title {
        color: #262626;
        font-size: 1.5em;
        line-height: normal;
        font-weight: 700;
        margin-bottom: 0.5em;
    }
    
    .small-desc {
        font-size: 1em;
        font-weight: 400;
        line-height: 1.5em;
        color: #555;
    }
    
    .go-corner {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        position: absolute;
        width: 2em;
        height: 2em;
        overflow: hidden;
        top: 0;
        right: 0;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff8b8b, #d62828);
        border-radius: 0 4px 0 32px;
    }
    
    .go-arrow {
        margin-top: -4px;
        margin-right: -4px;
        color: white;
        font-family: courier, sans;
    }
    
    .card {
        display: block;
        position: relative;
        max-width: 300px;
        max-height: 320px;
        background-color: #f8f8f8;
        border-radius: 10px;
        padding: 2em 1.2em;
        margin: 12px;
        text-decoration: none;
        z-index: 0;
        overflow: hidden;
        background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #fca5a5, #ffb8b8);
        box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }
    
    .card:before {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        z-index: -1;
        top: -16px;
        right: -16px;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #d62828, #ff8b8b);
        height: 32px;
        width: 32px;
        border-radius: 32px;
        transform: scale(1);
        transform-origin: 50% 50%;
        transition: transform 0.35s ease-out;
    }
    
    .card:hover:before {
        transform: scale(28);
    }
    
    .card:hover .small-desc {
        color: #333;
    }
    
    .card:hover .card-title {
        color: #000;
    }
    
    .flex-container {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-evenly;
        margin-top: 75px;
    } 

    h1 {
        color: #d62828;
        text-decoration: solid;
    }

    .quotation {
        font-style: italic;
        margin-top: 20px;
        color: #ffffff;
    }

    /* Media Queries for Responsive Design */
    @media screen and (max-width: 768px) {
        .flex-container {
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
        }
        .card {
            max-width: 90%;
        }
    }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="top-bar">
        <img class="logo" src="https://i.ibb.co/VDHvzFH/oss-logo-h-1.png" alt="SuperCool Logo">
        <p class="quotation">"Creativity is intelligence having fun." - Albert Einstein</p>
    </div>
    <header class="header">
        <div class="wave-container">
            <svg class="wave" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 1440 320"><path fill="#273036" fill-opacity="1" d="M0,288L48,266.7C96,245,192,203,288,181.3C384,160,480,160,576,181.3C672,203,768,245,864,250.7C960,256,1056,224,1152,224C1248,224,1344,256,1392,272L1440,288L1440,0L1392,0C1344,0,1248,0,1152,0C1056,0,960,0,864,0C768,0,672,0,576,0C480,0,384,0,288,0C192,0,96,0,48,0L0,0Z"></path></svg>
        </div>
        <br>
        <section class="flex">
            <h1>Propose Your Thinking</h1>
        </section>
    </header>
    <section class="flex-container">
        <div class="card">
            <p class="card-title">Start a Project <i class="fas fa-lightbulb"></i></p>
            <p class="small-desc">
                "The only way to do great work is to love what you do." - Steve Jobs
            </p>
            <div class="go-corner">
              <div class="go-arrow">→</div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <p class="card-title">Give an Idea <i class="fas fa-brain"></i></p>
            <p class="small-desc">
                "Don't be afraid of new ideas, be afraid of old ones." - Unknown
            </p>
            <div class="go-corner">
              <div class="go-arrow">→</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</body>
</html>
